flowchart LR
    A[Navigate to Microsoft Purview<br/>Information Barriers] --> B[Create Segment:<br/>Finance Department<br/>department -eq 'Finance']
    B --> C[Create Segment:<br/>HR Department]
    C --> D[Create Policy:<br/>Finance-HR Block Policy<br/>Assigned: Finance Dept<br/>Blocked: HR Dept]
    D --> E[Set Policy Status: Active]
    E --> F[Create Policy:<br/>HR-Finance Block Policy<br/>reverse direction]
    F --> G[Run Policy Application]
    G --> H{Application Status}
    H -- ApplyInProgress 0% --> H
    H -- PendingCompletion 100% --> H
    H -- Completed 100% --> I[Verify via PowerShell<br/>Get-EXOInformationBarrierRelationship]
    I --> J{Communication1To2 /<br/>Communication2To1}
    J -- Both False --> K[Validate in Microsoft Teams<br/>Attempt chat message]
    K --> L[Result: Failed to send<br/>Barrier confirmed enforced]
    J -- Either True --> M[Investigate: policy not<br/>fully applied / segment mismatch]
    M --> G
